flowchart TB
    Hosts([Services / Hosts])
    Agent[Collector / Agent<br/>scrape or push]
    Stream[("Event Stream<br/>(smoothing buffer)")]
    Writers[Write Workers<br/>batch + downsample]
    TSDB[("TSDB<br/>Hot SSD 7d / Warm HDD 90d /<br/>Cold Object Store 1y")]
    Query[Query Engine]
    Eval[Alert Evaluator]
    Router[Alert Router<br/>group, silence, route]

    Hosts -->|metrics| Agent
    Agent --> Stream
    Stream --> Writers
    Writers --> TSDB
    TSDB --> Query
    TSDB --> Eval
    Query -->|dashboards| Hosts
    Eval -->|firing| Router
    Router -.->|notify| Hosts

    classDef external fill:#1e2533,stroke:#3a4a6e,color:#cfd6e6
    classDef service fill:#1a3a2e,stroke:#3a6e54,color:#cfe6d6
    classDef store fill:#1e2a3e,stroke:#3a5a8e,color:#cfdcef
    classDef config fill:#3a2e1a,stroke:#6e5a3a,color:#efdfcf

    class Hosts external
    class Agent,Writers,Query,Eval,Router service
    class Stream,TSDB store
